OL,3,CMan and woman charged with murder of
OL,4,C21-month-old boy
OL,6,FA man and woman have been charged with
OL,7,Fthe murder of a toddler in December
OL,8,F2023.
OL,10,FOmiel Gordon, 35, and Shalom Morgan,
OL,11,F23, have also been charged with
OL,12,Fcausing or allowing the death of a
OL,13,Fchild and child cruelty.
OL,15,FPolice were called to an address in
OL,16,FMulberry Avenue in Leicester by East
OL,17,FMidlands Ambulance Service on 29
OL,18,FNovember 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
