OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777363547
OL,3,CMan and woman charged with murder of
OL,4,C21-month-old boy
OL,6,FTobias, who was 21 months old, was
OL,7,Ftaken to hospital but died on the 2
OL,8,FDecember 2023.
OL,10,FGordon from Butterwick Drive in
OL,11,FLeicester, and Morgan from Morledge
OL,12,FStreet in Leicester, were first
OL,13,Farrested in November 2023 following
OL,14,FTobias' admission. to hospital.
OL,16,FFamily liaison officers have been
OL,17,Fproviding support to the father of
OL,18,FTobias throughout the investigation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
