CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777363547
OL,3,CMan and woman charged with murder of
OL,4,C21-month-old boy
OL,6,FGordon and Morgan were charged on
OL,7,FMonday morning (27 April) and are due
OL,8,Fto be appearing at Leicester
OL,9,FMagistrates Court today.
OL,11,F"A complex investigation"
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Kevin Hames said:
OL,14,F"My thoughts very much remain with
OL,15,FTobias and everyone who is affected by
OL,16,Fhis extremely sad death.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
