OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777363547
OL,3,CMan and woman charged with murder of
OL,4,C21-month-old boy
OL,6,F"I am aware of the impact this news
OL,7,Ftoday will have in the community and
OL,8,Fwe will have officers in the areas
OL,9,Faffected to help in offering
OL,10,Freassurance to you - please do speak
OL,11,Fwith them if you have any concerns.
OL,13,F"This is a complex investigation and I
OL,14,Fdo want to thank those who have
OL,15,Fprovided support during this time. As
OL,16,Fcourt proceedings are now active, we
OL,17,Fdo ask that people do not speculate
OL,18,Fand take care with any publication
OL,19,Fmade so as to not prejudice these
OL,20,Fcourt proceedings".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
